  Amanda, 51, looked half her age as she posed up a storm in the Heart Radio offices this morning before sharing the snaps with her 1.8 million Instagram followers. She could be seen showing off the leaf-print green and white co-ord, which came from JD Williams UK. The star credited her stylist Karl Willett and personal assistant Adele Pentland for her subtle curls and youthful makeup look. She accessorised with a few bangles around one wrist, as well as a couple of rings.   